      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely stunning and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it\u2019s professionally detailed regularly. It drives like an absolute dream and honestly feels brand new inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take a look!",
