    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable E46 M3, a definitive masterclass in atmospheric induction. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response and a linear power band to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile, short-throw engagement. The chassis is structurally flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and a limited-slip M-differential ensuring optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. Every suspension kinematic, from the bushings to the dampers, remains in factory-spec tolerances, offering the communicative steering feel and mid-corner poise these icons are known for. This is a zero-compromise, collector-grade specimen with all preventative maintenance\u2014including rod bearings and VANOS servicing\u2014fully addressed.",
      "price": 48500.0,
